function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if string.find(Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idActor), "spider_adult") then
		table.insert(tSpiders, idActor)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	if #tSpiders > 0 and Hydra.ActorGroupGetCount("DRV_MonsterSpawn_Spider") < 1 then
		for i, idSpider in pairs(tSpiders) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpider) then
				idChosenSpider = idSpider
				
				Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idChosenSpider, "DRV_MonsterSpawn_Spider")
				
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idChosenSpider, false)
				
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(idChosenSpider, idJumpLoc, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, false)
				Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idChosenSpider, idLootCorpse)
				Hydra.QActorPower(idChosenSpider, S_ANIM_SPIDER_MOUNT)
				
				Hydra.EventSend("Spider_Found", idSelf)
				
				break
			end
		end
	end
end
